{
  "stem": "10829.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And most of the time, we'd have a few people would get killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The city life was-- one that was-- it was strict.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We would get up in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We'd go to either to cheder, or we would study.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I mean, that's all we knew in those days, is-- is study.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You have to go to cheder, and you have to study, and you have to work in the field and get ready for Yom Tov.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And you work almost all week to get ready for Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And this is the type of life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And once, twice a week, we would go down to the [NON-ENGLISH], to the-- to the bazaar or market and trade.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But we constantly lived in the fear of-- of being attacked by the Polacks or by the Urkaines.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They used to come down and search.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But we had a very good policeman who used to come in and used to help out a lot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And my dad was good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And my grandfather was just about the richest man in town in that time, Katz [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "My-- my zaide, when he walked to-- to the-- to the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Ukraines, to the villages down there, they used to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He always carried a ax with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Matter of fact, when he came to America, he still carried that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He always carried an ax with him, and he'd just as soon kill you as talk, and they knew that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "My zaide was-- [NON-ENGLISH] was his Jewish name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And when he walked, you know, the beard with a [NON-ENGLISH], with a black belt and the hat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "He was a religious man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Everybody there was religious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But he was deadly when you walked around him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And he had a lot of land.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
